<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="discrimination-n">discrimination <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪˌskrɪmɪ'neɪʃn/    美 /dɪˌskrɪmɪ'neɪʃn/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>歧视；区别对待：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>age / sex discrimination</strong>
年龄/性别歧视</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It seemed as if the battle against <strong>racial discrimination</strong> was gradually being won.
反对种族歧视的斗争似乎渐渐取得了胜利。</p><footer>人教⑩ – 3</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>识别力；辨别力：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He showed great discrimination in his choice of friends. 
他在择友方面颇具慧眼。</p></div></div>